-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_billing.sql
```sql
-- Deduplicate billing_events to one row per subscription + event_month (most recent event_id)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        subscription_id,
        event_month,
        amount,
        event_type,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY subscription_id, event_month
            ORDER BY event_id DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_billing_events') }}
)
SELECT
    subscription_id,
    event_month,
    amount,
    event_type
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- models/intermediate/int_user_industry.sql
```sql
-- Enrich users with company industry (LEFT JOIN to preserve users without company)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        u.user_id,
        c.industry
    FROM {{ ref('stg_users') }} u
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_companies') }} c
        ON c.company_id = u.company_id
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

-- models/intermediate/int_subscription_details.sql
```sql
-- Enrich subscriptions with plan tier (LEFT JOIN to preserve subscriptions with missing plans)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        s.subscription_id,
        s.user_id,
        s.started_at,
        s.ended_at,
        s.status,
        p.tier
    FROM {{ ref('stg_subscriptions') }} s
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_plans') }} p
        ON p.plan_id = s.plan_id
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

-- models/mart/fct_monthly_subscription_metrics.sql
```sql
-- Aggregate monthly subscription metrics by month, tier, and industry
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        b.event_month AS month,
        COALESCE(s.tier, '(unknown)') AS tier,
        COALESCE(u.industry, '(unknown)') AS industry,
        COUNT(DISTINCT s.subscription_id) AS active_subscriptions,
        SUM(b.amount) AS total_mrr,
        COUNT(DISTINCT s.user_id) AS unique_users
    FROM {{ ref('int_deduped_billing') }} b
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_subscription_details') }} s
        ON s.subscription_id = b.subscription_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_user_industry') }} u
        ON u.user_id = s.user_id
    GROUP BY
        b.event_month,
        COALESCE(s.tier, '(unknown)'),
        COALESCE(u.industry, '(unknown)')
)
SELECT * FROM source
